\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But there is a problem and the problem is there are almost always two voices in our head pulling us in two different directions.\uc0\u8232 \
